    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します\n{user}さんにお話があります",
      "startTime": 4.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さん？　どうかしたのか",
      "startTime": 6.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "あー、また鈴村さん言うて、他人行儀やわ～\nうちと{user}さんの仲やんかぁ",
      "startTime": 15.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば下の名前で呼ぶ約束だったな\n分かったよ、ゆ……優……",
      "startTime": 21.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "んー、まだぎこちないなぁ\nもっとはっきり言ってもらわんと聞こえへんよ",
      "startTime": 29.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かったよ、優\n……これでいいか？",
      "startTime": 35.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……下の名前で呼ぶの、早く慣れて下さいね",
      "startTime": 37.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "今度間違えたら、罰として吐息多めな甘く囁くイケボで\nうちの名前を呼んでもらいますからね",
      "startTime": 48.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_06_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ちょっと聞いてみたいかも……",
      "startTime": 51.8,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}